detaileddescription.para: An array which will convert JavaScript key codes into FKeys. The JavaScript key code should be used as an index into the array to perform the lookup. https://www.cambiaresearch.com/articles/15/javascript-char-codes-key-codes http://keycode.info/ Most key codes use the standard values given in the links above, but some have been choosen specially for 'right' versions of the same key.
